45  double calculate() {
46  double const p1 = inletPressure + 13.63 * barometricPressure;
47  double const x = (outletPressure - inletPressure) / p1;
48  double const z = ((6362 * moverShaftPower / flowRate) / p1) * ((specificHeatRatio - 1) / specificHeatRatio);
